        <heading>52.  Effects of termination of curatorship</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 52.  Effects of termination of curatorship
Upon termination of the curatorship, the curator is bound to account for his management and to restore the property to the formerly absent person or to his successors.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
